<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT19-B05-64</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA095-001025-B009-95</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://mdsg.umd.edu:80/MDSG/Communications/MarineNotes/Summer95/side3.html 129.2.110.45 19970215000742 text/html 6358
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 00:07:54 GMT
