<H1>Environmental Finance:<BR>
The Issue At A Glance</H1>

<DL>
<DT><IMG SRC="../../../../GIFs/blueball.gif" ALT="[*]" BORDER=0> The Goal
<DD>To reduce the flow of nutrients into the Chesapeake Bay by 40% and to hold it there.<P>
<DT><IMG SRC="../../../../GIFs/blueball.gif" ALT="[*]" BORDER=0> The Challenge
<DD>To raise an estimated $60-90 million a year to pay for the new or expanded Tributary Strategies programs to accomplish this goal.<P>
<DT><IMG SRC="../../../../GIFs/blueball.gif" ALT="[*]" BORDER=0> The Problem
<DD>How to pay the bill, if current taxes do not cover the shortfall.<P>
</DL>
<IMG SRC="GIFs/glance1.gif" ALT=""><BR>
