<HTML>

<HEAD>

<TITLE>Virginia Mason - Foundation</TITLE>

<META NAME="KEYWORDS" CONTENT="virginia mason foundation, medical research,
health care, virginia mason, medical, hospitals,
research">

</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="back.gif" BGCOLOR="#ffffff" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000ff" VLINK="#0000ff">

<TABLE BORDER="0" CELLPADDING="6" CELLSPACING="0" WIDTH="572">
        <TR>
                <TD COLSTART="1" COLSPAN="1" ROWSTART="2" ROWSPAN="1"VALIGN="TOP">
<IMG SRC="logo2.gif"><IMG SRC="logoc.gif">

                </TD>
                <TD COLSTART="2" COLSPAN="1"  ROWSTART="2" ROWSPAN="1">
	</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


<TABLE BORDER="0" CELLPADDING="6" CELLSPACING="0" WIDTH="565">

<tr>
                <TD COLSTART="1" COLSPAN="1" ROWSTART="1" ROWSPAN="1" WIDTH="75" VALIGN="TOP">
                </TD>
                <TD COLSTART="2" COLSPAN="2" WIDTH="490" VALIGN="TOP">
<center>
<font size=4>MAKING A DIFFERENCE AT VIRGINIA MASON</font>
</center>
	</TD>
	</tr>

        <TR>
                <TD COLSTART="1" COLSPAN="1" ROWSTART="1" ROWSPAN="1" WIDTH="75" VALIGN="TOP">
                </TD>
                <TD COLSTART="2" COLSPAN="1"  ROWSTART="1" ROWSPAN="1" WIDTH="340">
<font size=4 color="#2222c2">F</font>or more than 75 years, people throughout the region have turned to Virginia Mason Medical Center with the toughest health problems.
<p>
<font size=4 color="#2222c2">A</font>lthough it's not our motto, you will often hear it said, "If anyone can diagnose and cure it... it'll be the people at Virginia Mason."  Earning this reputation didn't happen without planning, hard work, and community support.
	</TD>
                <TD COLSTART="3" COLSPAN="1" WIDTH="150" VALIGN="TOP">
	<IMG SRC="vline.gif" ALIGN="left">
<font size=4>Contents</font><br>
	<Font Size=2>
                        <P><A HREF="give.htm"><IMG SRC="drop.gif" border=0> How to Give</A></P>
                        <P><A HREF="events.htm"><IMG SRC="drop.gif" border=0> Events</A></P>
                        <P><A HREF="funds.htm"><IMG SRC="drop.gif" border=0> Donations at Work</A></P>
                        <P><A HREF="vol.htm"><IMG SRC="drop.gif" border=0> Volunteer</A></P>
                        <P><A HREF="tax.htm"><IMG SRC="drop.gif" border=0> Tax-Advantaged Giving</A></P>
               </font> 
		</TD>
</TR>
<tr>
                <TD COLSTART="1" COLSPAN="1" ROWSTART="1" ROWSPAN="1" WIDTH="75" VALIGN="TOP">
                </TD>
                <TD COLSTART="2" COLSPAN="2"  ROWSTART="1" ROWSPAN="1" WIDTH="490" VALIGN="TOP">
<hr>
		</TD>
</TR>
	
</table>



<TABLE BORDER="0" CELLPADDING="4" CELLSPACING="0" WIDTH="565">
        <TR>
                <TD COLSTART="1" COLSPAN="1" ROWSTART="1" ROWSPAN="1" WIDTH="75" VALIGN="TOP">
                </TD>
                <TD COLSTART="2" COLSPAN="1" WIDTH="490" VALIGN="TOP">
<center>
<font size=2><b>HERE IS JUST A SAMPLE OF WHAT YOU HELP US ACCOMPLISH.....</b></font>
<br>
<IMG SRC="accom.gif" border=0>
</center>
<p>
<font size=2 color="#2222c2"><b>YOU HELP US CARE FOR CANCER PATIENTS</b></font><br>
Virginia Mason is dedicated to early detection and treatment. As one of the top 25 cancer treatment centers in the U.S., we diagnose more cancer cases than any other healthcare facility in the Northwest.
<p>
<font size=2 color="#2222c2"><b>YOU PROVIDE SUPPORT FOR THE TREATMENT OF DIABETES.</b></font><br>
The Benaroya Diabetes Center at Virginia Mason is the oldest and largest diabetes program in the Northwest. Each year, specialists help more than 2,500 people.  Hundreds of patients complete an advanced five-day diabetes education program, including some who attend on scholarships funded by gifts to the Medical Center.
<p>
<font size=2 color="#2222c2"><b>GIFTS FROM THE HEART, FOR THE HEART.</b></font><br>
Virginia Mason Heart Center physicians are working closely with researchers to find safer, more cost effective procedures. We were one of the first medical centers to use cardiac catheters to treat abnormal heart rhythms, which can now be cured without open heart surgery.
<p>
<font size=2 color="#2222c2"><b>YOU MAKE LIFE BETTER FOR KIDNEY PATIENTS.</b></font><br>
Virginia Mason surgeons have performed over 1,000 kidney transplants, more than all other Northwest hospitals combined. Our kidney transplant program is regularly ranked among the top 20 in the U.S.
<p>
<font size=2 color="#2222c2"><b>YOU FUND IMPORTANT NEW RESEARCH.</b></font><br>
Scientists at the Virginia Mason Research Center are expanding the boundaries of human knowledge in fields such as genetics, diabetes, cancer and rheumatology research. They are involved in exciting new work in the search for causes and cures of autoimmune diseases. Grants and donations help fund nearly 100 ongoing research projects.
<p>
<font size=2 color="#2222c2"><b>YOUR GIFTS MAKE NEW SURGICAL PROCEDURES POSSIBLE.</b></font><br>
Virginia Mason surgeons today are performing surgeries unheard of just a few years ago. Nuclear medicine, lithotripsy, stereotactic needle breast biopsy, lung volume reduction surgery and cochlear implants were all introduced to this region under the auspices of Virginia Mason. As a non-profit institution, VM relies on the generosity of its donors to stay on the leading edge of medicine.
<p>
<font size=2 color="#2222c2"><b>YOU OFFER HOPE TO PEOPLE WHO NEED A HELPING HAND.</b></font><br>
We believe in community service. With your help, Virginia Mason provides more than $17 million each year in uncompensated care for the general public. Some of the ways we help promote a healthier community include Tender Loving Care, a day care program for mildly ill children in the community; midwifery coverage in community clinics; and community partnerships that help provide for the most pressing health needs of at-risk youth.
<p>
<font size=2 color="#2222c2"><b>YOU HELP ENSURE QUALITY HEALTH CARE FOR WOMEN.</b></font><br>
Virginia Mason continues to offer a holistic approach to treating women. We were the first medical center in Seattle to have a core needle breast biopsy machine, which significantly reduces the pain and trauma of breast biopsies. Our Women's Health Center is committed to providing a caring, comfortable environment where women can count on getting the top-quality care they deserve.		</TD>
        </TR>
 <TR>
                <TD COLSTART="1" COLSPAN="1" ROWSTART="1" ROWSPAN="1" WIDTH="75" VALIGN="TOP">
         </TD>
                <TD COLSTART="2" COLSPAN="2"  ROWSTART="1" ROWSPAN="1" WIDTH="490">
<p>
<center>
<a href="give.htm">Make a Difference at Virginia Mason</a>
<P>
<a href="/cgi-bin/imagemap/navbar.map"><img src="../images/vmbar2.gif" ismap border="0"></a></center>
<hr>
		</TD>
        </TR>
</table>
</HTML>
