<center>
<font size=4>Receiving a Lifetime Income</font>
</center>
	</TD>
	</tr>

        <TR>
                <TD COLSTART="1" COLSPAN="1" ROWSTART="1" ROWSPAN="1" WIDTH="75" VALIGN="TOP">
                </TD>
                <TD COLSTART="2" COLSPAN="1"  ROWSTART="1" ROWSPAN="1" WIDTH="490">
<font size=4 color="#0000FF">C</font>haritable annuities and trusts provide a quarterly income for life, then benefit the medical center according to your wishes.  Up-front tax deductions and the possible lowering of your estate taxes are added benefits.  As little as $10,000 can fund an annuity.  Trusts are generally funded with businesses, real estate, stocks or cash.
<p>
<font size=4 color="#0000FF">L</font>et us know about your contribution.  Provide the information below and a Foundation representative will contact you by phone.  As important as your contribution is, the feedback and information through this site is crucial to the future of Virginia Mason.
	</TD>
