<p>
<b>Knab, John</b>: <i>60 mg Mepivacaine is Not an Adequate Intravenous Test Dose</i>.  American Society of Regional Anesthesia Twentieth Annual Meeting, Orlando, FL, March 30 - April 2, 1995
<p>
<b>Wills, Robert</b>:  <i>Postdural Puncture Headache Following Spinal Anesthetic with 25 gauge Whitacre, 24 gauge Sprotte, and 27 gauge Whitacre needles</i>. American Society of Regional Anesthesia Twentieth Annual Meeting, Orlando, FL, March 30 - April 2, 1995
<p>
<b>Gerancher, JC</b>:  <i>Fentanyl Prolongs Lidocaine Spinal Anesthesia Without Prolonging Recovery</i>. American Society of Regional Anesthesia Twentieth Annual Meeting, Orlando, FL, March 30 - April 2, 1995
<p>
<b>Hutchinson, Chad</b>:  <i>Hyperbaric Lidocaine:  Do Patient Characteristics and Block Techniques Influence Subarachnoid Spread?</i> American Society of Regional Anesthesia Twentieth Annual Meeting, Orlando, FL, March 30 - April 2, 1995
<p>
