<HTML>
<HEAD>
 <TITLE>VMMC Department of Urology - No Scalpel Vasectomy</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="../../images/vmbg.gif" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#00000">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="60%">
<img hspace="15" src="../../images/vmsqlog2.jpg" align="middle"><img src="../images/noscapl.GIF" align="middle">
<p>
<table width=85%>
 <tr>
  <td width="80"><img src="../../images/blank.gif" alt="" width="80" height="1"></td>
</center>
  <td>
<h1 align=left>What Every Man Should Know About It</h1>
<pre>

</pre>
<p>
<ul>
<li><a href="question1.html">What is a vasectomy?</a></li>
<li><a href="question2.html">Will a vasectomy affect a man's masculinity?</a></li>
<li><a href="question3.html">Who should have a vasectomy?</a></li>
<li><a href="question4.html">How does a vasectomy work?</a></li>
<li><a href="question5.html">What happens during a vasectomy?</a></li>
<li><a href="question6.html">And following the surgery  . . .?</a></li>
