<DOCHDR>
http://www.vmmc.org:80/vmrc/acru/ArthritisResearch.html 199.238.227.2 19970208013911 text/html 5525
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sat, 08 Feb 1997 01:38:16 GMT
