of glutamic acid decarboxylase.<P>

<b>Jo Wright</b> - Screening for ATM mutations in AT families, functional
studies of ATM.<P>

<b>Charlie Yeo</b> - Cloning genes for human minor histocompatibility 
antigens.<P>




