<DOCNO>WT19-B05-190</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA055-000919-B008-427</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.vmmc.org:80/vmrc/bkwok.html 199.238.227.2 19970208015811 text/html 4202
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sat, 08 Feb 1997 01:57:15 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
