Founded in 1984 by Pam and George Smith, whose daughter 
Rebecca has A-T, the A-T Medical Research Foundation 
(A-TMRF) is a private, non-profit organization whose sole 
purpose is to fund medical research that may lead to a cure 
for ataxia-telangiectasia.<P>
