<H1><CENTER>Mission Statement</CENTER></H1>
<center><IMG ALIGN=bottom SRC="vmbbarw.gif"></center>
<center><table  WIDTH="75%">
<tr><td><b><font size=+1>The Department of Radiology is committed to providing accurate, efficient, cost effective, timely diagnostic information and therapeutic procedures which enable medical care providers to meet the needs of their patients.<BR><BR>
Our team provides peronalized and innovative services to our patients and providers in a caring and professional manner.<BR><BR>
We believe our educational programs and investment in people provide our patients with qualitycare, our community with skilled professionals and our employees with opportunities for professional growth and job enrichment.<BR><BR>
</font></td></tr>
</table></center>
