<H1><CENTER>Value Statement</CENTER></H1>
<center><IMG ALIGN=bottom SRC="vmbbarw.gif"></center>


<H2><CENTER><P><B><I>SERVICE</I></B></P></CENTER></H2>
<center><table  WIDTH="75%">
<tr><td><b><font size=+1>We Deliver personalized and courteous service to all our customers: 
 We serve patients.  Our most important customer is the patient -- in all that we do the patient comes first.<BR><BR>
We serve health care providers, both at VMMC and in the  community.  We do this with efficiency, courtesy and respect.<BR><BR>
We serve each other.  Our success hinges on teamwork among sections of our Department, and between physicians, technical staff and support staff.
</font></td></tr>
</table></center>
<center><IMG ALIGN=bottom SRC="vmbbarw.gif"></center>

<H2><CENTER><P><B><I>TEAMWORK</I></B></P></CENTER></h2>
<center><table  WIDTH="75%">
<tr><td><b><font size=+1>Teamwork is the essential characteristic of our Department. 
Teamwork consists of communication, flexibility, courtesy and mutual respect for every member of the team.
</font></td></tr>
</table></center>
<center><IMG ALIGN=bottom SRC="vmbbarw.gif"></center>

<H2><CENTER><P><B><I>EXCELLENCE</I></B></P></CENTER></h2>
<center><table  WIDTH="75%">
<tr><td><b><font size=+1>We define excellence as combinig skill, innovation,creativity,
professionalism and compassion.  We expect this excellence of  all our staff, believing that it is an essential part of patient care.<BR><BR>
</font></td></tr>
</table></center>
<center><IMG ALIGN=bottom SRC="vmbbarw.gif"></center>
<CENTER><IMG  SRC="radbar1.gif" USEMAP="#radbar"ismap border="0"></CENTER>
<MAP NAME="radbar">
<AREA SHAPE= RECT COORDS= "0,0,95,62" HREF="Mission.htm">
