<HEAD>
<TITLE>Conferances </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="vmbg.gif" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#00000">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="60%">
<img hspace="15" src="vmsqlog2.jpg" align="middle"><IMG ALIGN=bottom SRC="vrad.gif"><br>

<center>
<br><img src="radres2.gif" alt="VMMC Radiology Residency">
</center>
<center><HR  SIZD=3 width=65%></center>

<pre><CENTER><H3><b><i>    Conferences and Lectures</i></b></h3></CENTER></pre>

<center><TABLE BORDER="0" CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="0" WIDTH="85%">
<tr>
     <td><h4>             There is a very full schedule of teaching conferences and lectures throughout the year
                 for radiology residents. These include formal lectures here and at the University of Washington,
                 case conferences some of which are presented by staff and some by residents, section 
                 meetings with presentation of interesting cases, and local meetings of regional and national
                 radiologic societies.
</H4></td>
</table></Center>

<pre><CENTER><H3><b><i> Intradepartmental Conferences</i></b></h3></CENTER></pre>
<center><TABLE BORDER="0" CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="0" WIDTH="75%">
<tr>     <Td valign=top width = 5%><IMG ALIGN=top SRC="blueball.gif"></Td>
              <Td ><H4>Weekly radiology departmental conferences for thorough discussion of interesting                               cases and diagnostic problems.</H4></td>
<tr>     <Td valign=top width = 5%><IMG ALIGN=top SRC="blueball.gif"></Td>
              <Td ><H4>Didactic lectures</H4></td>
<tr>     <Td valign=top width = 5%><IMG ALIGN=top SRC="blueball.gif"></Td>
              <Td ><H4>Mock oral conference per week where attending shows unknown cases to                               residents in a"hot seat" format.</H4></td>
<tr>     <Td valign=top width = 5%><IMG ALIGN=top SRC="blueball.gif"></Td>
              <Td ><H4>Resident case conference each week where the residents show each other                              interesting cases from their services.</H4></td>
<tr>     <Td valign=top width = 5%><IMG ALIGN=top SRC="blueball.gif"></Td>
              <Td ><H4>Journal Club once a month to review current radiologic literature</H4></td>.
<tr>     <Td valign=top width = 5%><IMG ALIGN=top SRC="blueball.gif"></Td>
              <Td ><H4>Introductory summer lecture schedule that covers the basics of radiology.</H4></td>
<tr>     <Td valign=top width = 5%><IMG ALIGN=top SRC="blueball.gif"></Td>
              <Td ><H4> Clinical case conferences with Medicine and Surgery staffs.

</H4></td>
</table></Center>
<CENTER><H3><b><i>Interdepartmental Conferences</i></b></h3></CENTER>
<center><TABLE BORDER="0" CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="0" WIDTH="85%">
<tr>
     <td><h4>Our radiology residents participate in many clinical conferences where the radiologist, pathologist
                  and clinical attending staff meet to discuss interesting cases.  These include GU Conference,
                  Neuro Conference, Pulmonary Conference, Cardiology Conference, GI Conference, 
                  OB Conference, Musculoskeletal Conference and Tumor Board.
</H4></td></tr>
</table></Center>

<CENTER><H3><b><i>Other Conferences and Meetings</i></b></h3></CENTER>
<center><TABLE BORDER="0" CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="0" WIDTH="75%">
<tr>     <Td valign=top width = 5%><IMG ALIGN=top SRC="blueball.gif"></Td>
              <Td ><H4>Weekly Thursday afternoon lecture series at the University of Washington.  Our                                residents attend all the lectures, grand rounds and case conferences given on                                Thursdays from 3-6 pm in the UW Radiology Department.</H4></td></tr>
<tr>     <Td valign=top width = 5%><IMG ALIGN=top SRC="blueball.gif"></Td>
              <Td ><H4>Joint UW/VM conference each month to show interesting CT/MR cases.</H4></td></tr>
<tr>     <Td valign=top width = 5%><IMG ALIGN=top SRC="blueball.gif"></Td>
              <Td ><H4>Diagnostic Radiology Physics lectures at the University of Washington.</H4></td></tr>
<tr>     <Td valign=top width = 5%><IMG ALIGN=top SRC="blueball.gif"></Td>
              <Td ><H4>Monthly city-wide ultrasound conference at Virginia Mason.  This is the local  chapter
                    meeting of the American Institute of Ultrasound in Medicine (AIUM).</H4></td></tr>
<tr>     <Td valign=top width = 5%><IMG ALIGN=top SRC="blueball.gif"></Td>
              <Td ><H4>Meetingseetings of the Washington State Radiological Society, Pacific Northwest
                    Radiological Society and the Seattle Chapter of the Society of Nuclear Medicine.</H4></td></tr>

</table></Center>
<BR>
<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=2 CELLSPACING=2 CELLPADDING=2 WIDTH=80%>
