<CENTER><H3><b><i>Research</i></b></h3></CENTER><PRE><H4>
                         Residents are required to either submit a paper for publication or give a presentation at 
                         a regional or national meetingduring the course of their residency.  Residents are encouraged
                         to become involved with on-going clinical research projects either with radiology attending 
                         staff or clinical attending staff. Travel funds are available for residents presenting at major
                         medical meetings.  Some of the most recent publications and presentations include:

<CENTER><H3><B></B><I>Selected Publications by VMMC Radiology Faculty and Residents</I></H3></CENTER>

                        Coates GG, Eisenberg B, Dail DE.  99mTc sulfur colloid demonstration of diffuse pulmonary
                        interstitial extramedullary hematopoiesis in a patient with myelofibrosis: A case report and 
                        review of literature. Clinical Nuclear Medicine 1994; 19:1079.

                        Eisenberg B, Coates GG and Holder LR.  Tc 99m bone scan and MRI correlation in the
                        detection of occult bone infarction.  Clinical Nuclear Medicine 1994; 19:1045.

                        Eisenberg B, Coates GG, Gass MA, Sicuro PL, Lee ME and Taylor LP.  Indium-111 DTPA
                        cisternographic demonstration of magna cisterna magna.  Clinical Nuclear Medicine 
                        (In press Jan 1995).

                        Coates GG, Gass MA, Sicuro PL, Lee ME, Fellows CL and Eisenberg B.  
                        Gallium-67 citrate detection of infected automatic internal cardiac defibrillator. 
                        Journal of Nuclear Medicine Technology (Accepted May 1994).

                        Coates GG, Gass MA, Sicuro PL and Eisenberg B.  The "breast-pocket" sign: a clue
                        to the possibility of spurious radionuclide uptake.  Journal of Nuclear Medicine 
                        Technology ( Accepted May 1994).

                        Coates GG, Eisenberg B, Wong SC, Chu FWK, Picozzi VJ.  Tc-99m MDP detection of 
                        diffuse metastatic involvement of the liver by salivary gland mucoepidermoid carcinoma.  
                        Clinical Nuclear Medicine (Accepted October 1994).

                        Hashimoto BE, Kenny K, Kramer D.  Duplex and color doppler appearance of isolated
                        internal iliac aneurysm.  Journal of Ultrasound in Medicine 1992; 11:45.

                        Hashimoto BE, Kramer D and Brennan L.  Amniotic fluid volume: fluid dynamics and
                        measurement technique.  Seminars in US, CT and MR 1993; 14:409.

                        Hashimoto BE, Hayes AS and Ager JD. Sonographic diagnosis and treatment of ganglion 
                        cysts causing suprascapular nerve entrapment.  Journal of Ultrasound in Medicine  1994; 13:671.

                        Nodell CG, Freeny PC, Dail DH et al.  Serous cystadenoma of the pancreas with a metachronous 
                        adenocarcinoma.  American Journal of Roentgenology 1994; 162:1352.

                        Eisenberg B, Pepping M, Hanelin L, Althouse L, Beck P, Lee ME et al.  Tc99m HMPAO SPECT
                        compared to MR/CT and clinical assessment  in the diagnosis of dementia.  Clinical Nuclear
                        Medicine 1991; 16:711.

                        Eisenberg B, Lee ME, Lee R, and Breitz HB.  General Radiologic Principles: Nuclear Medicine.  
                        Gore RM, Levine MS and Laufer I (eds) Textbook of Gastrointestinal Radiology.  
                        W.B. Saunders, 1993.

                        Lee ME.  Breast Cancer Screening.  Agostini R (ed) Medical and Orthopedic Issues of Active
                        and Athletic Women. Hanley and Belfus, Inc. and Mosby, 1994.
                        Lee ME.  Radiographic Evaluation of Sports Related Injuries.  Agostini R (ed) Medical and
                        Orthopedic Issues of Active and Athletic Women. Hanley and Belfus, Inc. and Mosby, 1994.

                        Lee ME.  Radiopharmaceuticals and drugs in Nuclear Medicine.  A review of reactions, 
                        treatments and risk management.  Advance for Administrators in Radiology. 
                        Merim Publications, 1994.

                        Eisenberg B.  A Practical Guide to Imaging and Treatment of the Thyroid and Parathyroids. 
                        Churchill Livingstone, 1991.

                        Prekeges JL, Eisenberg B, Coates GG, Ryan JA, Lee R.  Computer analysis of Thallium 201/Tc99m
                        Parathyroid images.  Journal of Nuclear Medicine Technology 1995; 23:70.

                        Tzamaloukas AH, Murphy G, Eisenberg B.  Extraosseous calcifications in patients on chronic dialysis.
                         Int J Artific Organs 1994, 17:311.
         
                        Eisenberg B, Murata GH, Tzamaloukas AH, Zager PG.  Gastroparesis in diabetics on chronic dialysis.  
                        Nephron 1993.

                        Tzamaloukas AH, Murata GH, Zager PG, Eisenberg B. The relationship between glycemic control
                        and morbidity and mortality for diabetics on dialysis.  ASAIO 1993, 39:880.

                        Kunkel CF, Scremin AME, Eisenberg B.  Effect of standing on spasticity, contracture and osteoporosis
                        in paralyzed males.  Arch Phys Med Rehab 1993, 74:73

                        Scremin AM, Kunkel CF, Eisenberg B et al.  Physostigmine improves cerebral blood flow in human
                        focal cerebral ischemia.  Stroke 1993.

                        Carroll LL, Tzamaloukas AH, Scremin AE, Eisenberg B.  Hand dysfunction in patients on chronic
                        hemodialysis.  Int J Artific Organs 1993, 16:694.

                        Tzamaloukas AH, Gibel LJ, Eisenberg B, et al.  Scrotal edema in patients on CAPD. Dialysis and
                        Transplantation 1992, 21:581.

                        Elliott MW, Eisenberg B, et al.  Pitfalls in BMD evaluation by dual photon absorptiometry. 
                        Clin Nuc Med 1992,17:714.

                        Waldman J, Eisenberg B, et al.  Comparison of radionuclide automated and manually calculated
                        GFR in spinal cord injury patients.  Clin Nuc Med 1992, 17:958.

                        Tzamaloukas AH, Murata GH, Murphy G, Eisenberg B.  Hypoglycemia in diabetics on dialysis 
                        with poor glycemic control: hemodialysis Vs CAPD.  Int J Artific Organs 1992,15:390.

                        Arrington ER, Hartshorne Mf, Eisenberg B, et al.  The two view radionuclide ventriculogram: 
                        advantages of the LPO view.  Clin Nuc Med 1991,17:371.

                        Williamson WR, Quenzer RW, Rosenberg R, Meholic AJ, Eisenberg B, et al.  Appendicular 
                        osteomyelitis: diagnosis by .064 T MRI, three phase bone scanning and indium scanning with
                        biopsy proof.  Magnetic Res Imaging 1991, 9:945.

                        Tzamaloukas AH, Murata AH, Harford AH, Sena P, Eisenberg B, et al.  Hand gangrene in diabetic
                        patients on chronic dialysis.  ASAIO 1991,37:638.

                        Eisenberg B, Murphy G, Tzamloukas AH.  Sternal osteomyelitis complicating hemodialysis blood 
                        access.  Am J Physiol Imaging 1991, 6:26.

                       Haygood TM, Olander RL, Mosdell D, Eisenberg B.  An ectopic rim sign in hepatobiliary scintigraphy.
                       Am J Physiol Imaging 1991, 6:62.

                      Murphy G, Tzamaloukas AH, Eisenberg B, et al.  Intraperitoneal thrombolytic agents in relapsing or 
                      persistent peritonitis of patients of CAPD.  Int J  Artific Organs, 1991, 14:87.

                      Eisenberg B, Powe JE, Alavi A.  Cold defects in In-111 leukocyte imaging of osteomyelitis in the axial
                      skeleton.  Clin Nuc Med 1991, 16:103.

                      Eisenberg B, Tzamaloukas AH, Murata GH, et al.  Factors affecting bone mineral density in older 
                      men on chronic in-center hemodialysis.  Clin Nuc Med 1991, 16:30.

                      Letterie GS, Kramer DJ.  Intraoperative ultrasound guidance for intrauterine endoscopic surgery.  
                      Fertility and Sterility 1994, 62:3.

                      Nyberg DA, Hegge FN, Kramer DJ, et al.  Premaxillary protrusion: sonographic clue to bilateral 
                      cleft lip and palate.  Journal of Ultrasound in Medicine 1993, 12:331.

                     Nyberg DA, Kramer DJ, et al.  Prenatal sonographic findings of Trisomy 18: Review of 47 cases. 
                     J Ultrasound Med 1993,2:103.

                     Hashimoto BE, Kramer DJ, Kenny K.  Duplex and color doppler appearance of isolated internal 
                     iliac aneurysm.  J Ultrasound Med 1992, 11:45.

                     Nyberg DA, Mahony BS, Kramer DJ.  Paranasal echogenic mass: Sonographic sign of bilateral
                     complete cleft lip and palate before twenty menstrual weeks.  Radiology  1992,184:757.

                     Nyberg DA, Sickler GK, Hegge FN, Kramer DJ.  Fetal cleft lip with and without cleft palate:
                     US classification and correlation with outcome.  Radiology 195:677.

                     Sires BS, Geggel HS, Heffernan JT, Crane RD, Holds JB:  Use of demineralized bone as 
                     an osteoinductive orbital enucleation implant in the rabbit.  
                     Ophthalmic Plastic and Reconstructive Surgery 1993,9:112.

                     Letterie GS, Case KJ.  Intraoperative ultrasound guidance for hysteroscopic removal of
                     intrauterine foreign bodies.  Surgical Endoscopy 1993, 7:182.

                     Hauptmann E.  Pancreatic pseudocyst with fistula to the common bile duct: Radiologic diagnosis
                     and management.  GI Radiology 1992, 17:151.

                     Traverso LW, Hauptmann E, Lynge DC.  Routine intraoperative cholangiography and its 
                     contribution to the selective cholangiographer.  American Journal of Surgery 1994,167:464.

                     Hashimoto BE, Hattrick CW.  New method of adult transcranial doppler.  J Ultrasound Med 1991, 10:349.

                     Hashimoto BE, Botoman VA.  Ultrasound may improve utility of defecography.  Diagnostic Imaging 1991, 11:11.

                     Hashimoto BE, Botoman VA.  New challenge for endorectal sonography: Diagnosis of fecal incontinence.
                     J Ultrasound Med 1993, 12:375.

                     Hashimoto BE, Brennan L, Lewis GL.  New horizons for duplex color doppler.  
                     Advance for Administrators 1992, 2:16.

                   <CENTER><I><H3>  Selected Presentations by VMMC Radiology Faculty and Residents<B></B></H3></I></CENTER>

                     Pacific Northwest Radiological Society.  Kramer DJ, Kidd CR.  
