<DOCOLDNO>IA055-000919-B009-39</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.vmmc.org:80/vmrc/acru/ProsorbaStudy.html 199.238.227.2 19970208015850 text/html 4529
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sat, 08 Feb 1997 01:57:57 GMT
