<BR>
<P>These four reports by Winn Schwartau discuss the June 2 and June 9, 1996 London Time articles about alleged extortion on banks in England. Some surprising results. The story isn't over yet.</P>
<BR>
<UL>
<LI>June 1, 1996, Florida:<a href="uktale1.html-ssi">Tales From The UK: Part I</a><BR>
<LI>June 8, 1996, Venice, Italy:<a href="uktale2.html-ssi">Tales From The UK: Part II</a><BR>
