<P><I>This section of Infowar.Com will present work from the Military, the Defense Universities, and those people with an interest in C4I, C3I and C2. Don't forget to look at the <a href="../discuss/discuss.html-ssi">Discussion Groups</a>, off of Infowar.Com's Home Page. </I></P>

