 <LI><a href="http://www.infosecnews.com"> Infosecurity News</a>....check this out!!!
The web site for Infosecurity News contains selected articles, product
announcements and news compiled from the latest issue of the magazine for
the protection of information.  InfoSecurity News is also a print
publication to which one can subscribe via the Web page.  It is 
free pending qualification in US and Canada only.  Mexico and
other countries are charged subscription fees.<BR>
<BR>
 <LI>  URL for the  homepage of the U.S. Arms Control and Disarmament
Agency at <a href="http://www.acda.gov">http://www.acda.gov</a> Information on several important treaties is
posted here, including START I, START II, CFE, etc.<BR>
   ACDA also publishes the annual _World Military Expenditures and Arms
Transfers_ report, a useful document for information on military spending,
imports, exports, etc. This document and others are available at the home
page as well.<BR>
