<tr>
<td width=440>

<P><B><Center>No huge build up. No major ego trip. But enough people ask, so here's the bio, the pix and some articles. Enjoy. Thanks. <a href="MAILTO:winn@infowar.com">Winn@Infowar.Com</a> </Center></B>

<H4>Books</H4>
We don't sell 'em here, so we won't be asking for any money. The links get you to where you can get more info - or, you can always get them at your local bookstore. <BR>
<UL>
 
<LI><img border=0 src="book2.gif">Announcing the release of <a href="winnbook.html-ssi">"Information Warfare - Cyberterrorism:  Protecting Your Personal Security In the Electronic Age"</a> BY WINN SCHWARTAU<BR>
<BR>
<LI><A HREF="MAILTO:lstewart@ncsa.com">Information Warfare: Chaos on the Electronic Superhighway</A><BR>
The book that started it all. Originally published in 1994. HERF Guns. Hackers. Policy. The term Information Warfare was classified until . . . Take a look. (Order from 717.258.1816 or 212.780.0380 or your local bookstore.) Reviewers call 212.780.0380. Thanks.<BR>
<BR>
<LI><A HREF="MAILTO:jjeng@vnr.com">The Complete Internet Business Toolkit</A><BR> Complete A to Z on to do biz on the Net. Simple, sassy and co-written by famous ex-hacker, Chris Goggans. 5500+ Internet and security utilities. Banned from export from the United States. See why. (717.258.1816 or 212.780.6133<BR>
<BR>
<LI><A HREF="MAILTO:lstewart@ncsa.com">Terminal Compromise</A><BR>
Hard to get. Only a few left. Novel about computer terrorism before anyone believed such a thing existed. (717.258.1816)
<BR>
</UL>

