<td valign=middle width=440>
<center><h2>
Tools and Utilities

</h2>


</Center>
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td width=440>

<P>Infowar.Com will be offering a massively complete set of utililties all on one site, (Ours, of course) always accessible from this Page. You may bookmark it, but sign-on will still be required. (Hey, we have to justify our existence to our sponsors. Go figure. :-)</P>

<P>Over the coming weeks and months we'll be adding megs upon megs of tools and utlities for your perusal. (Figure 600MB within a few months.) All are available somewhere on the Net, and we don't charge a thing. (Please, send no cash.) Some are demos, some are shareware, some are cripple-ware, some are freeware. If you download files, we ask that you do two things.</P>

<OL>
<LI> PLEASE scan for viruses. We hereby make no guarantees about their cleanliness, but we did try. In other words, if you trash your machine, it's not our fault. We warned you. <BR><BR>

<LI> PLEASE adhere to the requests for payment and use by the developers. Good netiquette counts and keeps much of our industry thriving.<BR>
</OL>
All files are ZIP'd.

<h4>What's New</h4>

New utilities posted in the last week or so.
<P>These are helpful utilities for your collection. Download them, use them respect them and search them for nasty little infections. If you have some that you'd like to add, please send them in ZIP format to WebWarrior@Infowar.Com</P>
<BR>

TOOLKIT\UTILS                   [Miscellaneous useful utilities]</P>
<a href="http://www.infowar.com/iwftp/utils/acroread.zip">ACROREAD.ZIP</A> 
Acrobat PDF Viewer Ver 2.1<BR>
<a href="http://www.infowar.com/iwftp/utils/DVIMSW26.ZIP">DVIMSW26.ZIP</A> 
TeX DVI viewer for Windows<BR>
<a href="http://www.infowar.com/iwftp/utils/DVIWIN29.ZIP">DVIWIN29.ZIP</A>       
TeX DVI viewer and printer for Windows<BR>
<a href="http://www.infowar.com/iwftp/utils/DVIWN271.ZIP">DVIWN271.ZIP</A>      
Tex DVI viewer and printer for Windows<BR>
<a href="http://www.infowar.com/iwftp/utils/EDITOR10.ZIP">EDITOR10.ZIP</A>      
Binary and ASCII file editor<BR>
<a href="http://www.infowar.com/iwftp/utils/EDITPRO.ZIP">EDITPRO.ZIP</A>        
Windows based text and hex editor<BR>
<a href="http://www.infowar.com/iwftp/utils/FND-IT12.ZIP">FND-IT12.ZIP</A>       
DOS version of the UNIX commands grep, diff and find<BR>
<a href="http://www.infowar.com/iwftp/utils/GS261.ZIP">GS261.ZIP</A>          
Ghostscript editor for Windows NT<BR>
<a href="http://www.infowar.com/iwftp/utils/HELPED19.ZIP">HELPED19.ZIP</A>    
Windows help file generator<BR>
<a href="http://www.infowar.com/iwftp/utils/HZNET.ZIP">HZNET.ZIP</A>         
"HZ" coding for Chinese characters<BR>
<a href="http://www.infowar.com/iwftp/utils/INETLITE.ZIP">INETLITE.ZIP</A>      
Tools (spell checker, WWW page manager, etc)<BR>
<a href="http://www.infowar.com/iwftp/utils/LEM3205A.ZIP">LEM3205A.ZIP</A>    
VI editor for Windows 95 and NT<BR>
<a href="http://www.infowar.com/iwftp/utils/LI130.ZIP">LI130.ZIP</A>          
 File viewer\finder\editor<BR>
<a href="http://www.infowar.com/iwftp/utils/LI_BTA.ZIP">LI_BTA.ZIP</A>         
